value: Formerly occurred on the island of Sainte Marie and opposite mainland of eastern Madagascar, probably from the head of Antongil Bay southward to Tamatave. Now extirpated on the former island and said to be confined only to a few patches of forest between Fito and Maroantsetra. 1
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Resident, forest: small area NE Madagascar (extinct).
